# docs/ is AI-workflow-only (analysis-vN, plan-vN, prompts-vN, review-vN,
# charter, progress, pipeline-state, features-vN, etc.) — never committed.
# User-facing docs live in documentation/. Use `git add -f` to commit a
# specific docs/ file (rarely needed).
docs/
